"Geeqie és un visualitzador d'imatges lleuger per Linux, BSDs i compatibles."

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: ../data/org.geeqie.Geeqie.metainfo.xml.in:11
msgid ""
"It supports fast navigation using thumbnails, multiple windows, and full-"
"screen viewing. Images can be copied, moved, renamed, and deleted directly "
"from the interface."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: ../data/org.geeqie.Geeqie.metainfo.xml.in:12
msgid ""
"Geeqie provides tools for managing large image collections, including "
"keyword tagging, powerful search features, and a duplicate image finder. "
"Metadata such as EXIF information can be displayed as overlays on images."
msgstr ""

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: ../data/org.geeqie.Geeqie.metainfo.xml.in:13
msgid ""
"Additional features include slideshow presentations and remote control via "
"command-line scripts. Images are accessed directly from the filesystem "
"without the need for import."
msgstr ""

